 shows that the atom has a tiny nugget in the center,

15:03.480 --> 15:04.400
 which we call the nucleus,

15:04.400 --> 15:05.840
 which is a positively charged object.

15:05.840 --> 15:09.080
 So then by like 1910, 11, we have this model of the atom

15:09.080 --> 15:09.960
 that we learn in school,

15:09.960 --> 15:13.240
