 I guess three of them would be in the standard model,

31:09.900 --> 31:13.460
 like the weak, the strong, and the electromagnetic,

31:13.460 --> 31:14.540
 and then there's gravity.

31:14.540 --> 31:16.220
 And there's gravity, which we don't worry about that,

31:16.220 --> 31:17.040
 because it's too hard.

31:17.040 --> 31:17.880
 It's too hard.

