41:28.220 --> 41:29.820
 that had been invented in the 70s

41:29.820 --> 41:31.260
 and really make sure that it worked.

41:31.260 --> 41:36.260
 So actually by 1999, when this machine turned off,

41:36.380 --> 41:39.500
