42:09.980 --> 42:12.300
 both experimentally and theoretically.

42:12.300 --> 42:15.260
 On the other hand, it's like having a jigsaw puzzle

42:15.260 --> 42:17.100
 where every piece has been filled in.

42:17.100 --> 42:19.020
 You have this beautiful image, there's one gap

42:19.020 --> 42:22.860
